{{Quote|The Mountains of the Exalted. The Altar of Promises where the faithful gather each night to be Exulted lies before them. You shall see it tonight, when you attend devotions.|[[Veratil]], to [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]|<ref name="TPS">''[[The Paradise Snare]]''</ref>}}
The '''Altar of Promises''' was located on [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]], near [[Peace City|Colony One]] at the base of the [[Mountains of the Exalted]]. It was where the [[t'landa Til]] performed their sham religious rites. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] offered to construct a temple to [[Yun-Yammka]] nearby, because he wondered if the t'landa Til could affect [[Yuuzhan Vong]] as well.

